<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10011181>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Sonerila subumbellata J. Wai & J.-M. Hu.A. Habit, B. Smaller leaf showing both adaxial (left) and abaxial (right) surfaces, C. Inflorescence, D. Bracts showing variation, E. Flower, F. Petals showing both adaxial (left) and abaxial (right) surfaces, G. Stamen, H. Longitudinal section of a flower showing hypanthium, stigma, style and ovary, I. Fruit showing top view (above) and side view (below). All from J. Wai 2713 (PSU). Drawn by P. Tippayasri." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10011181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10011183>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Photos of Sonerila subumbellata J. Wai & J.-M. Hu. A. Habit and habitat, B. Inflorescences, C. Inflorescence in lateral view showing bracts, flowers and young fruits, D. Mature fruits, E. Seed, lateral view, F. Seed showing verrucose papillae and tubercles on antiraphal side. Photos by J. Sae Wai." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10011183/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

